Former state District Judge G . 
  Todd Baugh sparked widespread outrage in 2013 over comments suggesting that 14-year-old Cherice Moralez shared some responsibility for her rape by a teacher . 
  Baugh sentenced former teacher Stacey Rambold to just one month in prison in the case . 
  He was censured by the Montana Supreme Court for his comments and suspended from the bench for 31 days  . 
  Baugh has been chosen for a lifetime achievement award by his local bar association . 
 